Description: Provides a custom R code formatting style including soft alignment, 
    tidyverse indentation, pipe-at-start formatting, operator spacing, aligned 
    comments, wrapped comments, multi-line argument breaking, and git-aware 
    styling. Includes an RStudio Addin for one-click application of the style.
